* IF THE ACCOUNT IN FBNK.ACCOUNT TABLE DON'T HAVE THE VALUE FOR
* CATEGORY FIELD IN THE RANGE BETWEEN 6601 AND  6699                                -->>SHOW MESSAGE : ISN'T A CERTIFICATE


