* THE VALUES IN RANGE BETWEEN 6601 AND 6699 AND DO NOT EXIST IN
* FBNK.AZ.ACCOUNT TABLE THEN                                                        -->>DELETE THE RECORD EXISTING IN FBNK.ACCOUNT.LIQUIDATION
